Subtitle of House Bill 1193
TO REQUIRE AN INSURER TO INCLUDE A LIENHOLDER ON PAYMENTS MADE
UNDER AN INSURANCE POLICY.
______________________________________________________________________
Amendment No. 1 to House Bill 1193
Amend House Bill 1193 as engrossed H1/30/25 (version: 1/30/25 10:34:33 AM):
Page 1, delete lines 29 and 30, and substitute the following:
"(b) This section does not apply to a lienholder that:
(1) Does not have a physical location in the state; or
(2) Has a physical location in the state, but:
(A) The claim for damages to a motor vehicle is less than
two thousand five hundred dollars ($2,500); or
(B) The payment is made directly to a repair facility for
the amount of the repairs."
